string->format

javatpoint.com/java-string-format

- like sprintf() in C
- alternatively: System.out.printf()

two variants
    - public static String format(String format, Object... args)  
    - public static String format(Locale locale, String format, Object... args)

format specifiers
    - %c: char
    - %d: integer
    - %f: floating point
    - %n: line separator
    - %s: string
    - %x: hex
